## Data Flow

<!-- {{#if tauri}} -->
### Desktop Data Flow

```
User Action
    → UI Component
    → Zustand Store (state update)
    → Service Layer (business logic)
    → Tauri Command (IPC)
    → Rust Backend (data validation)
    → Local Database (persistence)
    → Response → UI Update
```
<!-- {{/if}} -->

<!-- {{#if nextjs-aws}} -->
### Web Data Flow

```
User Action
    → UI Component
    → API Client (HTTP request)
    → API Gateway
    → Lambda Function
    → Business Logic
    → Database
    → Response → UI Update
```
<!-- {{/if}} -->

<!-- {{#if tauri-aws}} -->
### Hybrid Data Flow

**Local Operations**:
```
User Action → UI → Service → Tauri → Local DB → UI
```

**Sync Operations**:
```
Background Sync
    → Check Pending Queue
    → Send to Cloud API
    → Update Local State
    → Mark Synced
```
<!-- {{/if}} -->

